lgp.core.environment.dataset

Class Dataset<TData>

  • lgp.core.environment.dataset.Dataset<TData>
  • Type Parameters:
    TData - The type of the features in the input vector and the type of the outputs.

    public class Dataset<TData>

    A basic data set composed of a vector of input class Samples and a collection of outputs.

    NOTE: The type of the inputs and outputs is constrained to be the same.

    See Also:
    class Sample
